item.title: Searching for someone to Help me
item.dc:creator: @haviland4 haviland4
item.description:
@haviland4 wrote:

[quote=“Pure_, post:2, topic:541665”]Find the interface line ids using an interface editor, then send the line below ranging as magic. Then handle the button click, you’ll also need to keep track of which multi-use menu is open.

ie
show interface
set multi-use id to PICK_STARTER
button handling - if multi-use id == PICK_STARTER: do …[/quote]

could ya give me a hand?? via skype :palm:
